The Quesa was described as a quesadilla but seemed very different to me as I would describe it as a Mexican GINACOTTI or fried Calzone.
We shared an all vegetable one stuffed with an assortment of vegetables including spinach and cheeses.
It was very tasty and I like anybody would enjoy it.
